item.title: Yup, I used to be in OpTic (CoD4 Montage)
item.description:
Yup, I used to be in OpTic (CoD4 Montage)
I'm uploading this because I see comment arguments all the time on this topic, and because I liked editing the montage and how it turned out :D I was in OpTic for a few months around this time last year. I played hundreds of 1v1 snipes and a shit ton of ProMod Sim (console version of PC ProMod) but generally stayed away from the competitive sniping deal. I think I only played in one team sniper matches. They reminded me too much of sniper lobbies and I never really saw the point of them, even though I never really verbalized that. OpTic is a great group of guys and H3CZ is one of the most standup dudes on XBL and YouTube. Not to mention that they have Dtreats, which few people can honestly deny is hands down the most talented sniper on Xbox. I'm pretty good with a sniper rifle, but i'm admittedly very inconsistent. I have off days where I do horribly and end up rage quitting after going negative 3 matches in a row, and I have days where I can't miss. In the end, I don't want anyone to get the impression that I think I'm a pro at this game. I'm not. Never have and never will be. I play this game for fun, because it's fun. I suggest all of you do the same before you wind up basing too much of your self-esteem on Xbox. Anyways, I loved making montages and this one was no different. Hope you guys enjoy!
